org.hkijena.acaq5.api.traits

Interface ACAQTrait

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ACAQDiscriminator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ACAQDefaultDiscriminator, ACAQDefaultTrait, ImageIndexDiscriminator, ImageTitleDiscriminator

    public interface ACAQTrait
    Base interface for an algorithm data trait Traits are generated by data slots and accumulated over algorithm depth. Algorithms can modify output traits by adding or removing them.
